&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Fullstack Product Software Engineer on Dropbox’s Browse &amp;amp; Navigate Web Experience team, you will own and evolve the customer-facing web experiences and supporting systems behind Browse, Navigate, Preview, and related workflows. You will lead ambiguous, multi-phase work from technical discovery and design through rollout and operational ownership, partnering with Product, Design, Data, Infrastructure, and platform teams. You will combine full-stack execution with sound architecture, production judgment, and approved AI-assisted workflows while remaining accountable for final technical quality.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;Our Engineering Career Framework is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attrlink url author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;attrlink&quot; href=&quot;https://dropbox.github.io/dbx-career-framework/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-target-href=&quot;https://dropbox.github.io/dbx-career-framework/&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;viewable by anyone outside the company&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt; and describes what’s expected for our engineers at each of our career levels. Check out our blog post on this topic and more &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attrlink url author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;attrlink&quot; href=&quot;https://dropbox.tech/culture/sharing-our-engineering-career-framework-with-the-world&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-target-href=&quot;https://dropbox.tech/culture/sharing-our-engineering-career-framework-with-the-world&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;941429664724425756101444&quot;&gt;Own multi-phase full-stack product capabilities from requirements and technical design through staged rollout, measurement, and ongoing operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;914461558955940161119627&quot;&gt;Design and evolve scalable web experiences, services, APIs, and data models for Browse, Navigate, Preview, App Shell, window chrome, and shared web capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;696687199468472221950329&quot;&gt;Make architecture and scope tradeoffs that balance customer needs, delivery constraints, reliability, performance, security, privacy, and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;052547052244941431588023&quot;&gt;Improve observability, testing, incident readiness, and on-call health, and lead debugging and production-risk decisions when systems fail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;397392251465556919376070&quot;&gt;Use approved AI and automation tools for implementation, testing, debugging, documentation, and operational workflows; validate outputs and standardize practices that preserve engineering quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-usually-unique-id=&quot;501264521791609826850154&quot;&gt;Align cross-team dependencies and create leverage through reusable components and services, design and code reviews, runbooks, technical documentation, and mentoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
